ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 26th day of January, 2012, the Application for Leave to File Original Process and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus are DISMISSED. See 18 U.S.C. § 3231 (“district courts of the United States shall have original jurisdiction, exclusive of the courts of the States, of all offenses against the laws of the United States.”)
